comment._content: Lockheed Twins by Peter Marson/Air Britain has it as...Lockheed .#6386 A-29 (Hudson) 41-23569 USAAF delivered 1 February 1942. To RCAF BW707, Struck off charge 10 December 1947. Sold to UK owner in South Africa as ZS-DAF, believed crashed Stephenville, Newfoundland August 1946
